tcp: add snd_ssthresh stat in SCM_TIMESTAMPING_OPT_STATS

This patch adds TCP_NLA_SND_SSTHRESH stat into SCM_TIMESTAMPING_OPT_STATS
that reports tcp_sock.snd_ssthresh.

